ost_step.2: Determine the change due to sales. She sold 5 of them, so we subtract 5 from the initial amount: 19 - 5 = 14 cupcakes left.
ost_step.3: Note any additional cupcakes made. Maria made 10 more cupcakes.
ost_step.4: Add the new amount of cupcakes to the remaining number from Step 2. So, 14 + 10 = 24 cupcakes.
